{"type":"message","id":"37371b03","parentId":"34f7edfa","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:12:11.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主站显示\"登录\"按钮，说明主站也没登录。作家中心也需要登录。\n\n看来扫码登录保存的状态不能持久化，可能是因为番茄的登录验证比较严格。让我尝试在登录后直接获取作品信息，而不是依赖保存的状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看起来扫码登录保存的状态无法持久化。让我在登录后直接获取作品：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p9uom991kjwa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/website-automation/scripts && node -e \"\nconst WebsiteAutomation = require('./automation');\nconst { getConfig } = require('./config');\n\nasync function main() {\n  const config = getConfig('fanqie');\n  config.headless = false;\n  const auto = new WebsiteAutomation(config);\n  await auto.init();\n  \n  await auto.goto('https://fanqienovel.com/main/writer/login');\n  await auto.sleep(3000);\n  await auto.screenshot('before_login');\n  console.log('请扫码登录...');\n  \n  // 等待登录成功并跳转\n  for (let i = 0; i < 180; i++) {\n    await auto.sleep(2000);\n    const url = auto.page.url();\n    if (url.includes('book-manage') || url.includes('writer') && !url.includes('login')) {\n      console.log('登录成功! URL:', url);\n      await auto.sleep(3000);\n      \n      // 获取作品\n      const text = await auto.page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText);\n      console.log('作品页面:', text.slice(0, 1500));\n      break;\n    }\n    if (i % 15 === 0) console.log('等待中...');\n  }\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);\n\" 2>&1","timeout":400}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":619,"output":432,"cacheRead":52989,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54040,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773389519364}}
